lt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t<div><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/about_loop_02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t<div><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/about_loop_03.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t<div><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/about_loop_04.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\t\t\n\t<section id=\"facility-area\">\n\t\t<p class=\"facility-ttl anim anim-fadeinUp\">施設・サービス</p>\n\t\t<div class=\"facility-box wedding anim anim-fadeinUp\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-box-img\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/wedding_main_img_sp.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-text\">\n\t\t\t<h3>ウェディング<span class=\"h3_small\"> / WEDDING</span></h3>\n\t\t\t<p>一生に一度の特別な日、お二人の細部へのこだわりを叶えるウェディングプランナーと理想の結婚式を。</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://gran-suite.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/gransuite.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp anim-delay2\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://duo-cerezo.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/duocerezo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp anim-delay3\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://www.bienveil-h.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/bienveil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"facility-box ceremony anim anim-fadeinUp\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-box-img\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/ceremony_main_img_sp.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-text right\">\n\t\t\t<h3>ご葬儀<span class=\"h3_small\"> / CEREMONY</span></h3>\n\t\t\t<p>上越エリア最大、9つの葬儀ホールを運営。大切な人との最後のお別れの時、残される方の想いに寄り添い、心よりお手伝いいたします。</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://heian-ceremony.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/heian.png\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"facility-box event anim anim-fadeinUp\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-box-img\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/event_main_img_sp.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-text\">\n\t\t\t<h3>ご宴会・イベント<span class=\"h3_small\"> / EVENT</span></h3>\n\t\t\t<p>特別な日を印象的に。心に残る宴会やイベントは、柔軟なプランと細やかなサービスの宴会プランナーへお任せください。</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://duo-cerezo.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/duocerezo_others.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp anim-delay2\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://gran-suite.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/gransuite_others.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"facility-box other anim anim-fadeinUp\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-box-img\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/other_main_img_sp.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-text right\">\n\t\t\t<h3>その他<span class=\"h3_small\"> / OTHER</span></h3>\n\t\t\t<p>日常を彩る様々なサービスも展開。快適なカフェ、便利なコインランドリー、充実のカルチャースクールをぜひ。</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://r-sb.jp/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/regina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp anim-delay2\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/elc/\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/elc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"facility-btn anim anim-fadeinUp anim-delay3\"><a class=\"zoom\" href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/members/#thewash\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/thewash.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\t\t\n\t<section id=\"members-area\">\n\t<div class=\"wrapper anim anim-fadeinUp\">\n\t<div class=\"members-tex\">\n\t<h3 class=\"\">へいあんメンバーズ<span class=\"h3_small\"> / HEIAN MEMBERS</span></h3>\n\t<p class=\"lead\">月々1000円〜の掛け金で<br>ご家族の負担を軽減し「もしも」に備える</p>\n\t\t<p>葬儀は突然必要になることが多く、<br>\n\t費用負担も決して安いものではありません。<br>\n\t今から掛金を行い、費用を事前に準備することで「もしも」の時も安心です。<br>\n\tへいあんメンバーズはご葬儀に限らず、さまざまなシーンでご利用可能。<br>\n\tこの機会に、ぜひご検討ください。</p>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"members-img sp\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/heian_members_img.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t\t\n\t<a class=\"btn members-btn\" href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/members/\">詳しくはこちら</a>\n\t<div class=\"members-futai\">\n\t<p class=\"members-futai-ttl\">へいあんメンバーズならもっとお得なサービス</p>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/every/\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/members_logo_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\n\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/elc/\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/members_logo_2.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"members-img pc\"><img src=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/wp-content/themes/heian-corp/assets/img/heian_members_img.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\t\t\n\t<section id=\"contact-area\">\n\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t<h3>お問い合わせ<span class=\"h3_small\"> / CONTACT</span></h3>\n\t<p>平安メンバーズの契約内容のご確認、ご家族の契約の確認、冠婚葬祭の事前相談などお気軽にご連絡ください。</p>\n\t<div class=\"contact-supportcenter\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"contact-supportcenter-tex\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>お客様サポートセンター</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"num\"><a href=\"tel:0255247122\">025-524-7122</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"att\">受付時間：9:00〜17:00（土日を除く）</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<a class=\"btn contact-supportcenter-btn\" href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\n\t</main><!-- #main -->\n\n\n\t<div class=\"footersub\">\n\t\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/members/\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"footer-sub-large\">へいあんメンバーズ</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p>お申し込み・資料請求</p>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<!--<a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/hoken/\">-->\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.memoleadlife.co.jp/product/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>わずかな負担で家族に安心を</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"footer-sub-large\">はじめやすい葬儀保険</p>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t<li>\n\t \t\t<a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/every/\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>へいあんメンバーズだけの<br class=\"pc\">付帯サービス</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"footer-sub-large\">Every -エブリィ-</p>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/elc/\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>学びたい放題の<br>カルチャースクール</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"footer-sub-large\">ENJOY LIFE CLUB</p>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t\n\t<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n\t\t<div class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/\">ホーム</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/outline/\">会社案内</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/members/\">へいあんメンバーズ</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"//ten.1049.cc/tp/heian-co/\" target=\"_blank\">採用情報</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/pp/\">各種方針</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/contact/\">お問合せ</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.heian-co.jp/links/\">リンク集</a></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"footer-img\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"